<p class="v2-structure-link"><b>Message Structure:</b> <a href="StructureDefinition-SIU_S12.html">SIU_S12</a></p>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This message notifies other applications that an existing appointment has been modified on the filler application. This trigger event should only be used for appointments that have not been completed, or for parent appointments whose children have not been completed.</p>
